  <Content>The worst has come, our scouts report that the defensive lines at the Grass Fields are failing.  The Goblin Army has become overwhelming, we cannot hold them much longer. What I say will seem staggering, but... they will be upon Loures shortly. Do not be dismayed, we are preparing for their assault. Defensive points will be placed at three locations, the Front Gate, at the center of Loures Market, and at the Rear Gate. King Bruce...,no, all of Loures ask that any able Aisling, come help protect the capitol city of Temuair.

Dealos,
Loures General


